    <item>
      <title>关税忧虑和美国经济走强导致美元下跌预期短暂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/dollar-drop-seen-brief-amid-tariff-worries-us-economic-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们押注，鉴于美国经济相对强劲以及贸易战可能迫使投资者进入避险资产的背景，周二美元的暴跌可能是短暂的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/dollar-drop-seen-brief-amid-tariff-worries-us-economic-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 16:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战影响担忧超过伊朗制裁 油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国和中国之间的贸易战将损害全球经济增长的担忧超过了对伊朗加强制裁的宣布，油价小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
